{"tid":2066571,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"本來香港人同97年後出世港人後代都會有英籍","createTime":"2020-06-16T11:08:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-16T17:08:59.000Z","uid":41846,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"63e6fa538deb38be92e9cc7b7c2824494fdaace2","tid":2066571,"uid":41846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T11:08:23.000Z","msg":"你知道原本香港人同97年後出世港人後代都會有英籍嗎？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=646658022554221&amp;id=180641289155899\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D646658022554221%26id%3D180641289155899&d=St%2FdMm9ieZWtYGJEeV6aa29Dn5prBKp8mj11ELPip4s%3D&h=23e06146\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=646658022554221&amp;id=180641289155899</a><br />\n<br />\n提返先，下面所講英籍並非今日BNO <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n／／香港人英籍身份一直為中英談判期間一個重要議題。據英國解密檔案所示，香港行政局非官守議員曾於一九八四年二月上書倫敦，指出香港人希望可於主權移交以後，繼續世代保持BDTC身份，亦希望可以保持寫有香港字眼護照（即BDTC（HK）），希望倫敦可以代為向中國表達香港人意願。<br />\n<br />\n未幾，倫敦回覆指談判小組本原已將爭取港人延後英籍納入談判項目，雖然倫敦表明將盡力爭取，但亦警告指中國會予以反對，故倫敦提出後備方案 &ndash; 保留BDTC（HK）一切功能，但變改名稱，以換取中方妥協，例如British Associated Citizens（未有正式譯名）。<br />\n<br />\n如倫敦預計，無論BDTC後方案抑或換湯不換藥之後備方案，中國均不予接受，並表達中國對香港人國籍立場，即一切香港華人將於一九九七年七月一號自動附加中國國籍。為回應中國頑固立場，倫敦轉移以香港人有權與英國保持某程度適當地位為名，指出不可剝奪香港人英籍，雙方協商之下，中國將不承認此新英籍為正式英籍，只視為旅遊證件，重伸香港華人由此至此皆係中國籍，即使其人自出世起已因香港關係成為英國屬土公民（Ingrams，1952；香港前途研究計劃，2017）。倫敦對此表示諒解，雙方同意日後除於香港特別行政區及中國其他地區外，新英籍護照持有者將享有英國領事保護權利。雙方對新英籍協議，確應於中英聯合聲明備忘錄。／／<br />\n<br />\n#不是BNO<br />\n<br />\n（節錄自《敬安再會一九九七》，第二章第二節，歸化英籍）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eqNDpbW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeqNDpbW.jpg&h=5e5e287b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/HongKongFP/status/1272761264477859840?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FHongKongFP%2Fstatus%2F1272761264477859840%3Fs%3D20&d=St%2FdMm9ieZWtYGJEeV6aa29Dn5prBKp8mj11ELPip4s%3D&h=5fb4ff3d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FHongKongFP%2Fstatus%2F1272761264477859840%3Fs%3D20&h=074dadc2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/HongKongFP/status/1272761264477859840?s=20</a>"},{"pid":"a8ec5e1f435b68edaf4862ea137e6da1b3cb3394","tid":2066571,"uid":146030,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T11:14:59.000Z","msg":"擺明係支那要香港人世代做奴隸<br />\n先唔比bno有居英權<br />\n英國食咗隻死貓三十幾年"},{"pid":"f7c71ab04b375e6c691dafecd6dba5549da32ded","tid":2066571,"uid":60321,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T11:15:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1a9839e7757636250dd69a878d0e4f6c7f53dd6","tid":2066571,"uid":273021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T11:23:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3689416c59e86b237f42707d998ac1a2118d29a","tid":2066571,"uid":158270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T12:16:44.000Z","msg":"原本冇我哋添"},{"pid":"d1eac572a59d4ed82be7574fcd417bfd0d713d76","tid":2066571,"uid":41846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T17:01:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"209c2d7eed70a5de92faaf770c2cf5e3b0abc6c7","tid":2066571,"uid":72197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T17:05:14.000Z","msg":"屌你老母真係千錯萬錯都係共產黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f6a44b0e10d5fd3d34d05abab0fcd082ba71ad7","tid":2066571,"uid":6142,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T17:07:02.000Z","msg":"根本全部都係支那搞既鬼，國藉綁架<br />\n由支那入左un開始就對香港郁手，唔比港人獨立公投又好，玫瑰園計劃又好"},{"pid":"43e4e2c573d4b210b2fba37b2721bae6927d0cba","tid":2066571,"uid":131282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T17:08:59.000Z","msg":"最衰都係熱狗"}]}